* BrightBlade watched the fight from her tree limb, she chuckled to herself. 
How silly both the Maximals and Predacon traitors looked as they fought each 
other, she sighed...all she needed now was a carton of pop corn!*

" This is getting good!"

* She snarled with glee but then opened her comlink to Hell Beast, they had 
found Megatron's location and it was time to report!*

" My Lord Hell Beast, Gangon and I had located the stinking traitor 
Megatron. The local is Sector Gen, coordinates 392.665 North. Are there any 
further orders in which to give me, My Lord?"

* BrightBlade had incrypted her transmission so that it couldn't be 
traceable by and Maximal or traitorous bots, only Hell Beast would know how 
to decrypt it! She waited silently for word from her commander.*
